<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='595584' id='t-595584'>and what's remarkable about digital commonses</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597937' id='t-597937'>is you don't need a big percentage if your sample size is big enough</span>
