<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='642477' id='t-642477'>And the reason that I got obsessed with this, besides the obvious family aspects,</span>
