<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='761187' id='t-761187'>And I've spent a lot of time around other commons.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='764211' id='t-764211'>I've been around the early web. I've been around</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='766891' id='t-766891'>the early creative commons world, and there's four things</span>
