</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='796951' id='t-796951'>And open doesn't mean that there's no money.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799616' id='t-799616'>Closed systems, corporations, make a lot of money</span>
