<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='828983' id='t-828983'>And if you'd like to build corporate structures on top of it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='832564' id='t-832564'>that's okay too. That's all in the consent,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='835710' id='t-835710'>so if you don't like those terms, you don't come in.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='838274' id='t-838274'>It's very much the design principles of a commons</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='841366' id='t-841366'>that we're trying to bring to health data.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='843960' id='t-843960'>And the other thing about these systems is that it only takes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='846939' id='t-846939'>a small number of really unreasonable people working together</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='850118' id='t-850118'>to create them. It didn't take that many people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='853300' id='t-853300'>to make Wikipedia Wikipedia, or to keep it Wikipedia.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='856772' id='t-856772'>And we're not supposed to be unreasonable in health,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='858840' id='t-858840'>and so I hate this word &quot;patient.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='861116' id='t-861116'>I don't like being patient when systems are broken,</span>
